      "author": "Mason",
      "change": "Container variant added to Section 2 (mixed-content body, ds-fab--md --default close, optional 0/1/2-button footer). Clear button removed from the multi-select variant — Apply&nbsp;(n) + X close is sufficient. fab.css and selection-pill.css linked."
